---
title: Veggie Bulgogi Bowls with Meatless Farm® and Gochujang Fried Rice
description: Salty, spicy and sweet; it's easy to understand why this Korean staple is so well loved, which is why we've created a veggie version. The quick gochujang fried rice will take this to the next level of divine!
